      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Spokane socialists have secured\na promise from Attorneys barrow\nand Richardson to lecture in this\ncity as soon as the Haywood trial\nis concluded and they are able to\nleave Boise. No definite date for\nthe lecture has yet been decided.\nThe attorneys who have defended\nHaywood will speak on economic\nconditions and labor interests from\nsocialist standpoint. They will\nalso speak in Seattle."
    }
